            <m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{E rSub { size 8{F} } = left ( {  {3}  over  {2} }  "."  {  {n}  over  {γ} }  right ) rSup { size 8{ {  {2}  over  {3} } } } } {}</m:annotation>
